{"tid":1795837,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【劫案頻生】直擊旺角彌敦道「金行街」 5小時零警巡邏","createTime":"2019-12-24T08:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:34:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c507ab63a3f86a72c454d612d64640044ba8b8b","tid":1795837,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"近日搶劫案頻生，珠寶金行及錶舖固然是賊人目標，凌晨有賊人連快餐店都不放過，可見本港治安每下愈況。《蘋果》今早在亞皆老街至登打士街一段彌敦道巡視，5小時內也沒有見過警員的蹤影。該段彌敦道南北行線，珠寶金行林立，但街頭警力卻與真空無異。<br />\n亞皆老街至登打士街一段彌敦道約600米長，南北行線共計有31間珠寶金行和錶行，如周生生、周大福及六福等。由今早9時至下午2時，記者來回踱步，也沒有見過一名警員巡邏。店舖於10時半、11時左右陸續開門，耀眼的珠寶首飾，逐一放到飾櫃，吸引途人駐足，但就是沒有見到警員。<br />\n至於昨日遇劫的油麻地上海街金行，今日有兩男一女職員返回，他們沒有回答記者提問，進入店舖後也拉上鐵閘，並沒開門營業，相信是回來善後而已。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191224/large/1577172073_34e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191224%2Flarge%2F1577172073_34e2.jpg&h=733f95d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191224/60412364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191224%2F60412364&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpocyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=f33b4081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191224%2F60412364&h=47a39f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191224/60412364</a>"},{"pid":"b910b1b1547746fd2f25e10353093ec691dbe961","tid":1795837,"uid":40146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"全部都自己人做<br />\n緊係唔出現"},{"pid":"38a41b941e2d672c6731aca2b1823e52ca1477e6","tid":1795837,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"驚方：已安排便衣警巡邏"},{"pid":"6ec509443d633d4ae3314ba051e660672a150c80","tid":1795837,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"